ecuador 's consum price rise 2.5 pct in februari ecuador 's consum price index rose 2.5 pct in februari to 562.4 ( base 1978 ) , the nation statist and censu institut said . the rise compar to a 1.8 pct rise in januari and a 2.5 pct rise in februari 1986. the institut said accumul overal inflat for the first two month of thi year wa 4.0 pct compar to 5.0 pct for the same period last year . inflat for the 12 month end februari 1987 wa 25.5 pct compar to 13.0 pct for the 12 month end februari 1986 .